data.description: This Meticulously Kept Smart Home Is Located In The Highly Desirable Cypress Mills. With A Very Spacious Split Floor Plan, This Beautiful 3 Bed 2 Bath Home Is Exactly What You Have Been Looking For. Gorgeous Open Kitchen With Large Pantry Overlooks Living & Dining Area, Making A Great Space For Entertaining. Immense Private Primary Suite Has A Walk-In California Closet For Plenty Of Storage, Large Bathroom With Glass Shower And Garden Tub To Relax And Soak Away Your Worries. The Primary Closet Opens Up To The Laundry Room For Easy Convenience. Spacious Secondary Bedrooms With Carpet And Standard Closets. Sliding Glass Door Exits Off To The Expanded Screened In Back Patio, With Plenty Of Space To Entertain. Step Out Back To The Large Fenced In Yard Perfect For A BBQ Or A Relaxing Evening.
